hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? keflex dosage for tooth infection That said, the details of the ADP report give more insight on how the United States is gaining way too many low paying jobs.  Jobs gains were in the service sector were 147,000 private sector jobs, again most of the job gains.  The goods sector gained 19,000 jobs.  Professional/business services jobs grew by 27,000.  Trade/transportation/utilities showed strong growth again with 54,000 jobs.  Financial activities payrolls decreased by -4,000.
